com.camsolute.code.camp.lib.contract

Interface HasOrderBusinessId

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    HasOrder, IsOrderPosition, OrderPositionInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OrderPosition

    public interface HasOrderBusinessId
    Objects that honar this contract provide the order business id value when requested and allow it to be updated. The order business id is the current business id of a business order. Objects must reference the business order object instance to ensure that the id value they provide is current.
    Author:
    Christopher Campbell
